  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "chapterTitle": "第一部分 死亡",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300074147_28_1607-1749",
          "range": "1607-1749",
          "rangeStart": 1607,
          "rangeEnd": 1749,
          "markText": "针对每一条假设，思考下面这三个问题：●这条假设是怎么来的？●有充足的理由留下它吗？●我能用更好的假设替代它吗？",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1726409688,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-15 22:14:48",
          "chapterUid": 28,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074147&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1607&rangeEnd=1749",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dc1326c0813ab8376g017276?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1607&rangeEnd=1749"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300074147_28_4789-4991",
          "range": "4789-4991",
          "rangeStart": 4789,
          "rangeEnd": 4991,
          "markText": "你最稀缺的资源不是时间或金钱，而是注意力。我们一次只能关注一件事，这就是为什么它的价值如此之高。如果你的注意力被切分得支离破碎，不由自主地被分配到无数个不同的方向，那你肯定记不住多少东西。你没法在想法之间建立关联，把点连成线，最后构建出新的观点——你没法思考。要解决这个问题，单纯意识到自己在做什么还不够，你需要主动决定自己做什么，不做什么。\n",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1725496376,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-05 08:32:56",
          "chapterUid": 28,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074147&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4789&rangeEnd=4991",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dc1326c0813ab8376g017276?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4789&rangeEnd=4991"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "第二章 弃旧",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300074147_9_1247-1275",
          "range": "1247-1275",
          "rangeStart": 1247,
          "rangeEnd": 1275,
          "markText": "放弃旧的，我会暂时失去平衡。可如果不放弃，我会失去自我。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1725494807,
